Package: bnplasso
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Shrinkage with a Nonparametric Bayesian Lasso
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Santiago", 
      family = "Marin", 
      role = c("aut", "cre"), 
      email = "santiago.marinardila@anu.edu.au", 
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-0086-3721")
    ))
Description: 
    Fit linear regression models with a Nonparametric Bayesian Lasso 
    (BNP-Lasso) prior, an adaptive and flexible shrinakge prior for
    Bayesian regression and variable selection. The package uses an efficient
    Markov chain Monte Carlo algorithm to generate draws from the posterior
    distribution of the model parameters. For additional details, please see 
    Marin et al. (2025+) <https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2411.08262>. 
